<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.376909>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Itaipusa sbui n. sp. A. General organisation (from a live specimen, completed with observations on sectioned material). B. Reconstruction of the proboscis and pharynx from the right-hand side. C. Reconstruction of the atrial organs from the right-hand side (B – C from a paratype). D. Copulatory organ (from the holotype)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/376909/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

